    EphesoftJobExecutor

    public class EphesoftJobExecutorImpl
extends org.activiti.engine.impl.jobexecutor.JobExecutor
implements EphesoftJobExecutor
    This class represents a job executor impelmenting Ephesoft's job executor interface and overriding third party's Default job Executor.
